AnalyticsWorkspaceId.description: The ID of the Tableau Next workspace the visualization is associated with.

DeveloperName.description: The API name of the visualization.

Language.description: The supported languages for the visualization. There are over 50+ supported language and dialect values.

LastDraftModifiedDate.description: The last modified date for the visualization in draft mode.

LastPublishedDate.description: The last published date for the visualization.

NamespacePrefix.description: The namespace prefix for the visualization.

OwnerId.description: The user ID of the user who created the visualization.

TemplateAssetSourceName.description: If the visualization was created from a template, this is name of the asset source.

TemplateSource.description: If the visualization was created from a template, this is name of the template.

Version.description: The API version for the visualization.
